Karl Heinrich Marx, illul deg 5 si [[Magu]] deg ussegwas 1818 di tmurt n Treves illan di Rhenanie tamurt n [[Lalman]] yemmut di 14 di [[Meɣres]] 1883 di temdint n Londres. Marx illa d argaz n tsertit u d-amesnagay ameqṛan, d netta id isnulfan ayen i wumi neqqar [[Tazdukla]] "le communisme", id yeqaren belli ulac amgarad ger imdanen γas ulamma yella deg ixeddim nsen n yal ass.

==Tameddurmant==
Ilul Karl Heinrich Marx di Treves asegwas n 1818. Yella d wis sin ger 8 Tam w-atmaten-is. Vava-s, Heinrich Marx (1782–1838), d-abugaṭu, yefrurid deg yiwet twacult twudayt Ackenaz. Jed-nsen Meier Halevi Marx yella dawday, m-ad mmi-s d warraw n mmi-s uγalen d-imasiḥiyen, ẓẓiẓrgen isem nsen γer Heinrich iwakken ad izmiren ad xedmen, yemma-s n Karl, Henriette Pressburg (20 [[Yulyu]] 1788-30 [[Wamber]] 1863), d tawdayt n [[Tamurt Bwadda|tmur bwadda]].

==Tizrawtin ines==
Yekcem γer Gymnasium Friedrich-Wilhelm n Treves asegwas 1830. m-id yebwi Abitur ines, yekcem γer tseddawit, di tazwara di Bonn [[tuber]] asegwas 1835 iwakken ad ilmed azref, dinna yebwid aselkin di tagara usegwas, sinna di [[Berlin]] di tseddawit Friedrich-Wilhelm si [[Meɣres|meγres]] 1836 yelhad kan d-[[Amezruy|umezruy]] d [[Tasnagayt|tesnagayt]], yekfa tizrawtin ines asegwas n 1841.

